@QueueSimulatorAPI_HostAddress = http://localhost:5196

### Test Root Endpoint
GET {{QueueSimulatorAPI_HostAddress}}/
Accept: application/json

###

### Test M/M/1 Calculation - Valid System (ρ < 1)
POST {{QueueSimulatorAPI_HostAddress}}/api/simulation/mm1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "meanInterarrivalTime": 2.0,
  "meanServiceTime": 1.5
}

###

### Test M/M/1 Calculation - Unstable System (ρ >= 1)
POST {{QueueSimulatorAPI_HostAddress}}/api/simulation/mm1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "meanInterarrivalTime": 1.0,
  "meanServiceTime": 2.0
}

###

### Test M/M/1 Calculation - Invalid Input (negative value)
POST {{QueueSimulatorAPI_HostAddress}}/api/simulation/mm1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "meanInterarrivalTime": -1.0,
  "meanServiceTime": 1.5
}

###

### Test M/M/1 Calculation - Example 2
POST {{QueueSimulatorAPI_HostAddress}}/api/simulation/mm1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "meanInterarrivalTime": 3.0,
  "meanServiceTime": 2.0
}

###
